original_title: Two dengue related deaths during past 24 hours
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Dengue Control Unit said two dengue related deaths have been reported during the past 24 hours.
A total of 36 dengue related deaths have been reported so far in 2023.
The highest number of patients, 26,702, have been reported from the Western Province.
